.TH manta-delete-images 1  "images " 
.SH NAME
manta\-delete\-images \- [experimental] Delete images
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmanta delete images\fR [\fB\-d\fR|\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIIMAGE_IDS\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
[experimental] Delete images
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-d\fR, \fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Simulate the operation without making changes
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIIMAGE_IDS\fR>
Comma\-separated image IDs to delete.
eg: e2ce82f0\-e7ba\-4f36\-9f5c\-750346599600,59e0180a\-3fdd\-4936\-bba7\-14ba914ffd34
